data.description: Stop by and see this beautiful home! With the home having 6 bedrooms and a beautiful, spacious kitchen, this home would be the perfect fit for your family. It also comes with a beautiful patio with built in grills and coolers. Keep the entertainment alive by gathering around the firepit and outdoor fireplace! Make this your new home!
